<br>
Ningel Bish<br>
30 Magician<br>
Solusek Ro <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uzorryn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zorryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 66<br> <font color=#333333>(3/24/01 6:08:10 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Bind in Oasis</span><hr size=1> I would bind at the pier in Oasis.  If you gate/port out, you can catch the raft to TD quickly there.  I think this is much faster than binding in FV or OT.<br>
<br>
Note: from the Golra island, it is very convenient to swim to the porting chamber to get around.<br>
<br>
Regards,<br>
Zorryn Neblin<br>
lvl44 Mage<br>
Terris Thule <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/usampox.showPublicProfile?language=EN>sampox</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_bluespot.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 74<br> <font color=#333333>(3/24/01 10:27:39 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthingstokill.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=174.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   i would say FV</span><hr size=1> Firiona seems much easier a place to bind in...the boat out of firiona goes right by the golra island...<br>
<br>
if you come from oasis you have a very long swim to get back...<br>
<br>
plus theres a bank right in FV..<br>
<br>
